# YT Music TUI

A beautiful terminal-based YouTube Music player for Linux.

![YT Music TUI](https://img.shields.io/badge/Linux-Fedora-%23354d20?logo=fedora)
![Python 3.11+](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.11+-blue?logo=python)

